question2

dino_data = datasaurus_dozen %>%
  filter(dataset == "dino")
library(ggplot2)
ggplot(data = dino_data, mapping = aes(x = x, y = y)) +
  geom_point()

dino_data %>%
  summarize(r = cor(x, y))
